data.description: Introducing an acclaimed residential development. This charming two-story house, recognized for its excellence, boasts a cottage-style design and an expansive open floor plan on the ground level. The kitchen is fully equipped with a breakfast bar, pantry, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, all seamlessly connected to the dining area. From the inviting family room, step through the elegant French doors that lead to a private backyard enclosed by a fence, where a patio awaits. Upstairs, you'll discover a full bathroom, a utility room, and three generously proportioned bedrooms. The master suite is a true retreat, featuring dual vanities, a spacious walk-in closet, a separate shower, and a luxurious garden tub.
